data.description: *Under Contract - Seller is accepting Back-Up offers.* Seller is eager to sell and willing to negotiate closing cost concessions or a rate buy down with approved offer. Welcome to your new Venetian Villa townhome. This desirable end-unit has been completely renovated and is move-in ready. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and 1337 sqft this home makes a perfect starter home or home for a growing family. Being STR eligible it would also make a great investment property. Downstairs you have an open concept  living/dining room with ceramic tile flooring. The kitchen has been upgraded with granite countertops and lots of cabinetry. you will find a half bathroom underneath the stairs. There is a covered porch overlooking your quiet, privacy fenced backyard perfect for entertaining guests. Upstairs you have the main bedroom with en-suite and an additional 2 bedrooms and another full bathroom. This townhome is centrally located, close to shopping, entertainment, restaurants and schools. Don't wait, come and see this home today! All information and measurements are approximate and should be verified by buyer.
